<h1 class="h1-responsive center mt0 mb4">1ROOF Privacy Policy</h1> <p>Underoneroof Ltd is the provider of <a target="_blank" href="http://www.1roof.com">www.1roof.com</a> and as a company, we take your privacy very seriously. We ask that you read this Privacy Policy carefully as it contains important information about what to expect when we collect personal information about you and how we will use your personal data.</p><p>Underoneroof Ltd’s principal place of business is 1 Fredericks Place, London EC2R 8AE.</p><p>This policy applies to information we collect about:</p><ul><li>visitors to our website <a target="_blank" href="http://www.1roof.com">www.1roof.com</a>; and</li><li>people who register for our service,&nbsp;including those asking for assistance on home improvement projects and the service providers quoting for the projects posted by them.</li><li>The information we collect about you</li></ul><p>When you register for our service we collect the following personal information from you:</p><p>Name, postal address, email address, telephone number and (if you are a business) your VAT number<br>If you log in to the service, we will access your Facebook Public Profile (which includes your Facebook username or userID, age range, your list of friends, as well as any information that you share with them). This information is collected by Facebook and is provided to us under the terms of Facebook’s privacy policy. You can control the information that we receive from Facebook using the privacy settings in your Facebook account.</p><p>Occasionally we may receive information about you from other sources (such as credit reference agencies) which we will add to the information which we already hold about you in order to help us target our service to you in the most appropriate way.</p><ul><li>How we will use the information about you</li></ul><p>We gather this information to allow us to process your registration, process any project quotes you may make or respond to, and